snippet.title: Headlice Chaos Trailer - Wishlist on Steam
snippet.description:
headlicegame.com

Headlice is the debut title from indie studio Bunguin Games. Play as a reverse-horror parasite looking for a host. Jump, swing, and chomp your way through a corporate hellscape in search of... the perfect cup of coffee
